                     <interp inst="t18240407-72-person684" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am apprentice to Mrs. Merrit, pawnbroker, Ratcliff-highway. I have two coats which the prisoner pawned on the 4th of March in the evening for 8 s., in the name of 
               <persName id="t18240407-72-person685">
                  Jack 
                  Brown
               <interp inst="t18240407-72-person685" type="surname" value="Brown"></interp>
